        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your sprayed slime thickens on contact with air, giving it some substantial stopping power and possibly even locking foes in place. When you use @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.ancestry-features.Item.Slime Squirt] or @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feats.Item.Slime Spray], creatures in the area must attempt a @Check[reflex|against:class-spell] save against the higher of your class DC or spell DC. On a failure, they become @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Clumsy]{Clumsy 1} for 1 round. On a critical failure, they become @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Clumsy]{Clumsy 2} and @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Immobilized] for 1 round.</p>"
        },
